OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPatchy fog and frost will soon
OL,6,Fclear to leave plenty of dry weather
OL,7,Ftoday with sunny spells. However,
OL,8,Fcloud will bubble up at times, perhaps
OL,9,Fallowing the odd light shower to break
OL,10,Fout. An easterly breeze developing.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA dry and settled night is
OL,13,Fexpected with clear periods. A touch
OL,14,Fof frost will form again in some rural
OL,15,Fareas, though the easterly wind will
OL,16,Falso freshen.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
