OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FAnother fine day is expected.
OL,6,FIt will remain dry with plenty of
OL,7,Fsunny spells. Feeling pleasant in the
OL,8,Fsunshine, though there will be a brisk
OL,9,Fand cooling easterly wind blowing.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FWindy
OL,12,Fon Wednesday. Some warm sunshine,
OL,13,Fthough a chance of some rain in the
OL,14,Ffar west. Mostly fine thereafter with
OL,15,Fsunny periods. Winds slowly easing.
OL,16,FPatchy overnight frosts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
